'''單一主神論'''（{{lang-en|Henotheism}}），源自希臘語的「{{lang|gre|'ἑνας θεός}}」（henas theos，意爲「單一神」），也稱'''單一神教'''<ref>{{cite web|title=《印度佛教史》第二节〈印度的宗教〉|url=http://fo.sina.com.cn/2012-08-28/1548491.shtml|website=新浪網|publisher=新浪佛學|date=2012-08-28|accessdate=2017-06-17|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513042650/http://fo.sina.com.cn/2012-08-28/1548491.shtml}}</ref>、'''尊一神論'''<ref>{{cite web|author=傅佩榮|title=《宗教哲學》第六講〈上帝的存在問題〉|url=http://ocw.aca.ntu.edu.tw/ocw_files/102S202/102S202_AA06L01.pdf|publisher=臺灣大學開放式課程|website=國立臺灣大學|accessdate=2017-06-17|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517023108/http://ocw.aca.ntu.edu.tw/ocw_files/102S202/102S202_AA06L01.pdf}}</ref>、'''單一神論'''<ref>{{cite thesis|title=韩国巫教的构造与中心思想|type=Ph.D|author=李浩栽|url=http://academy.tienti.org/binder/conf_004_14.pdf|publisher=中国社会科学院宗教研究所|accessdate=2017-06-17|website=天人研究總院|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624080832/http://academy.tienti.org/binder/conf_004_14.pdf}}</ref>、或'''單一多神論'''<ref>{{cite web|title=神学辞典 - 有神论|url=http://www.chinacatholic.net/book/html/131/7255.html|website=天主教在线|accessdate=2017-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619213443/http://www.chinacatholic.net/book/html/131/7255.html|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是指對某[[神_(一神教)|單一神]]的崇拜，且此種崇拜無須否定其他任何[[神|神]]的存在<ref name=britannicamonolatry>[http://www.britannica.com/topic/monotheism Monotheism] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/topic/monotheism |date=20200406201955 }} and [https://www.britannica.com/topic/polytheism Polytheism] {{Wayback|url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/polytheism |date=20080428102323 }}, Encyclopædia Britannica (2014)</ref><ref name=taliaferro78>{{cite book |author1=Charles Taliaferro |author2=Victoria S. Harrison |author3=Stewart Goetz |title=The Routledge Companion to Theism |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ct7fCgAAQBAJ |year=2012 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-136-33823-6 |pages=78–79 |access-date=2017-06-18 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819025650/https://books.google.com/books?id=ct7fCgAAQBAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哲學家[[弗里德里希·谢林|弗里德里希·谢林]]首先提出了這一概念，而後{{link-en|弗里德里希·威爾克|Friedrich Welcker}}使用了該詞以描述古代希臘人的原始[[一神論|一神論]]<ref>{{cite book|author= Robert Karl Gnuse |title= No Other Gods: Emergent Monotheism in Israel |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=pBSJNDndGjwC |year= 1997|publisher= Bloomsbury Academic |isbn= 978-1-85075-657-6 |pages= 132–133 with footnote 6 }}</ref>。

德國語文學家、東方學家[[馬克斯·繆勒|馬克斯·繆勒]]在其對{{link-en|印度諸教|Indian religions}}的研究中進一步拓寬了「Henotheism」一詞的含義<ref>Müller, Max. (1878) ''Lectures on the Origin and Growth of Religion: As Illustrated by the Religions of India.'' London:Longmans, Green and Co.</ref><ref name=alonp370>{{cite book|author1=Ilai Alon |author2= Ithamar Gruenwald|author3=Itamar Singer |title= Concepts of the Other in Near Eastern Religions |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=A1-l66daLgYC|date=1994 |publisher=BRILL Academic |isbn=978-9004102200 |pages=370–371 }}</ref>，例如[[印度教|印度教]]中的經文提及并贊頌了數個神明、并將其全部比擬爲一個單一且終極的神聖本體<ref name=taliaferro78/>。繆勒將單一主神論的概念應用於其對[[西方世界|西方]][[神學|神學]]與宗教[[例外論|例外論]]（與{{link-en|東方宗教|Eastern religion}}相較而言）的批評，指出某種文化上的[[教義|教義]]可以令一神論在本質上確立明確定義的同時又與不同類型之[[神的概念|神的概念]]相比有著與生俱來的優越性。

